
<p>This week, MacSparky is pleased to welcome back&nbsp;<a href="https://www.listenlater.net/?referrer=macsparky">Listen Later</a>&nbsp;as a sponsor. Listen Later is a service that transforms articles, emails, and PDFs into personalized podcast episodes using their advanced AI narrator. This allows you to listen to your reading list during commutes, workouts, or any time you&#8217;re on the go.</p>


